2
00:39:43,913 --> 00:39:45,613
Kikkerikii!

3
00:39:46,313 --> 00:39:49,313
Thank you all so much for coming to

4
00:39:49,313 --> 00:39:52,913
Takanashi Kiara and Ninomae Ina'nis'

5
00:39:52,913 --> 00:39:55,913
first concert, Day 2, Drawn to Dawn!

6
00:39:59,313 --> 00:40:02,313
I am Takanashi Kiara, and next to me is...

7
00:40:02,513 --> 00:40:04,113
Wah!

8
00:40:06,971 --> 00:40:10,171
Good morning, afternoon, evening everyone!

9
00:40:10,171 --> 00:40:11,971
This is Ninomae Ina'nis!

10
00:40:15,171 --> 00:40:19,171
That's right, it is finally time to start Day 2!

11
00:40:19,171 --> 00:40:21,171
Is everyone hyped?!

12
00:40:21,171 --> 00:40:22,671
Hype, hype, hype, hype!

13
00:40:22,971 --> 00:40:25,671
All right, before we kick things off, of course,

14
00:40:25,671 --> 00:40:28,171
we have some important safety rules

15
00:40:28,171 --> 00:40:29,971
and house guidelines to go over.

16
00:40:30,171 --> 00:40:32,671
First, photography and the use of

17
00:40:32,671 --> 00:40:35,171
recording equipment are strictly prohibited...

18
00:40:35,171 --> 00:40:38,671
...during the performance. However,

19
00:40:38,671 --> 00:40:40,171
if you are watching from home,

20
00:40:40,171 --> 00:40:41,671
screenshots are allowed.

21
00:40:41,671 --> 00:40:42,671
Please take lots of screenshots.

22
00:40:42,671 --> 00:40:45,171
スクショはOKですよ！
Screenshots are okay!

23
00:40:45,671 --> 00:40:48,171
Also, the venue is smoke-free,

24
00:40:48,171 --> 00:40:50,171
so please refrain from smoking inside.

25
00:40:50,671 --> 00:40:53,471
Unless you're smoking hot like me!

26
00:40:53,471 --> 00:40:56,171
We've heard that one before.

27
00:40:57,471 --> 00:40:59,671
If you start, un-feeling well...

28
00:40:59,671 --> 00:41:01,171
(I'm feeling well...)

29
00:41:01,171 --> 00:41:02,171
Unfeeling well!

30
00:41:02,171 --> 00:41:05,171
If you start feeling unwell at any point,

31
00:41:05,171 --> 00:41:06,671
please don't push yourself.

32
00:41:06,671 --> 00:41:08,671
Just reach out to the nearest staff member

33
00:41:08,671 --> 00:41:09,671
for help, and drink water.

34
00:41:10,671 --> 00:41:13,671
For everyone's safety, please avoid any

35
00:41:13,671 --> 00:41:15,671
dangerous or disruptive behavior.

36
00:41:15,671 --> 00:41:19,171
This once again, no matter how hyped it is,

37
00:41:19,171 --> 00:41:21,171
includes moshing, diving...

38
00:41:24,171 --> 00:41:26,671
...sitting on shoulders, jumping excessively,

39
00:41:26,671 --> 00:41:29,171
or throwing objects towards the stage.

40
00:41:29,171 --> 00:41:32,671
Climbing onto the stage, intentionally

41
00:41:32,671 --> 00:41:34,171
blocking the aisles,

42
00:41:34,171 --> 00:41:36,671
or rushing towards the front is not allowed.

43
00:41:36,971 --> 00:41:39,671
Please refrain from disruptive shouting,

44
00:41:39,671 --> 00:41:41,671
erratic lightstick movements,

45
00:41:41,671 --> 00:41:43,671
or any extreme motions that might interfere

46
00:41:43,671 --> 00:41:45,671
with the experience of those around you.

47
00:41:45,971 --> 00:41:47,371
Be considerate.

48
00:41:47,371 --> 00:41:50,171
If you don't follow the instructions of

49
00:41:50,171 --> 00:41:52,171
our staff, you may be asked to leave.

50
00:41:52,671 --> 00:41:55,171
Yeah, please keep in mind that the venue,

51
00:41:55,171 --> 00:41:57,671
organizers, performers, and staff...

52
00:41:57,671 --> 00:42:00,671
...cannot be held responsible for accidents,

53
00:42:00,671 --> 00:42:03,671
equipment damage, or trouble

54
00:42:03,671 --> 00:42:07,471
caused by failing to follow instructions.

55
00:42:08,171 --> 00:42:10,671
So you stumbled over the same words.

56
00:42:10,671 --> 00:42:13,671
It's hard, okay? I'm trying my best here.

57
00:42:13,671 --> 00:42:15,171
I can't read.

58
00:42:15,671 --> 00:42:18,671
Additionally, any costs for damage resulting

59
00:42:18,671 --> 00:42:20,671
from ignoring these rules

60
00:42:20,671 --> 00:42:23,171
will be the responsibility of the person.

61
00:42:23,671 --> 00:42:27,171
There are cameras in the venue for filming

62
00:42:27,171 --> 00:42:29,171
and photography today,

63
00:42:29,171 --> 00:42:31,671
and you might appear in the footage.

64
00:42:31,671 --> 00:42:34,671
These may be used for promotional purposes,

65
00:42:34,671 --> 00:42:37,171
so please keep that in mind.

66
00:42:37,171 --> 00:42:40,171
And finally, just like yesterday,

67
00:42:40,171 --> 00:42:42,171
the concert will be in two parts.

68
00:42:42,171 --> 00:42:45,671
There's a part for Wawa and a part for me,

69
00:42:45,671 --> 00:42:47,671
so please look forward to them!

70
00:42:50,671 --> 00:42:53,671
And yeah, that is it for the rules.

71
00:42:54,171 --> 00:42:58,171
The show is about to begin, so get ready!

72
00:42:59,171 --> 00:43:00,671
Have fun!

73
00:43:01,671 --> 00:43:03,671
See you soon, bye bye!

