146
00:51:57,475 --> 00:52:02,475
Hey everyone! Get ready to dance off for day 2! Are you ready?!

147
00:52:09,975 --> 00:52:12,975
古びた伝説は
The ancient legend...

148
00:52:12,975 --> 00:52:15,975
呪われた幽霊船に
...is on the cursed ghost ship.

149
00:52:15,975 --> 00:52:18,975
綴る夜の帳
Bound in the curtain of night.

150
00:52:21,675 --> 00:52:24,475
そこに富みが残る
The wealth remains there.

151
00:52:24,475 --> 00:52:27,475
海賊の夢があるのなら
If you have a pirate's dream,

152
00:52:27,475 --> 00:52:30,475
確かめないでしょう
surely you'll go check it out?

153
00:52:33,475 --> 00:52:36,275
海の仲間よ　若き娘よ
Comrades of the sea, young maidens,

154
00:52:36,275 --> 00:52:39,475
命を賭して　後悔に繰り出してやろう
stake your lives and set sail on the voyage!

155
00:52:39,475 --> 00:52:42,475
止まない　雨の弾丸で
With a ceaseless rain of bullets.

156
00:52:45,475 --> 00:52:48,475
眩しいほど　この瞳焦がす
Dazzling enough to scorch these eyes,

157
00:52:48,475 --> 00:52:51,475
生命の炎　茜の色彩
the flame of life, the color of madder red.

158
00:52:51,475 --> 00:52:54,475
払う　宝石なのなら
If it's a jewel to be paid...

159
00:53:00,475 --> 00:53:02,975
私のもの　そう私のもの
It's mine, yes, it's mine.

160
00:53:02,975 --> 00:53:05,975
命の証を
The proof of life,

161
00:53:05,975 --> 00:53:08,975
あなたの求める全てを
everything that you seek.

162
00:53:12,475 --> 00:53:15,475
輝くはず　全て錆びついて
It should shine, but everything rusts,

163
00:53:15,475 --> 00:53:18,475
それでも土塗れに　染み付くなら
yet if it remains covered in dirt,

164
00:53:19,475 --> 00:53:22,475
泡沫と共に　鎮め
