168
00:53:50,475 --> 00:53:53,475
満月の金銀珠玉
Gold, silver, and pearls of the full moon,

169
00:53:53,475 --> 00:53:56,475
七つの身の宝玉に
in the seven jewels of the sea,

170
00:53:56,475 --> 00:53:59,475
滾る無念共
along with seething regrets.

171
00:54:02,475 --> 00:54:05,475
綻び富みを狙う
Aiming for the fraying wealth,

172
00:54:05,475 --> 00:54:08,475
愚か者の身も知らず
not knowing the state of the fool,

173
00:54:08,475 --> 00:54:11,475
騒がし珍味を
a noisy delicacy.

174
00:54:14,475 --> 00:54:17,475
胸に当たる　黒い魂の群れ
Striking the chest, a flock of black souls,

175
00:54:17,475 --> 00:54:20,475
影の底で　忍び寄る亡者の渦
a vortex of the dead creeping at the bottom of the shadows,

176
00:54:20,475 --> 00:54:23,475
まるで　開かずの箱
just like an unopened box.

177
00:54:26,475 --> 00:54:29,475
手放したいわ　諦めたいわ
I want to let go, I want to give up,

178
00:54:29,475 --> 00:54:32,475
悪夢の中から　逃げられるのに
even though I could escape from this nightmare,

179
00:54:32,475 --> 00:54:35,475
まだ　戦ってる　夜を思い出したら
I'm still fighting; when I remember the night...

180
00:54:42,475 --> 00:54:44,975
私のもの　そう私のもの
It's mine, yes, it's mine.

181
00:54:44,975 --> 00:54:47,975
自分自身を　信じ込ませてしまって
I've made myself believe in it,

182
00:54:47,975 --> 00:54:50,975
縛り付けて　待って　気付いた
bound myself to it, and wait—I realized.

183
00:54:54,475 --> 00:54:57,475
夢の出口　永久の夜の鍵
The exit from the dream, the key to the eternal night,

184
00:54:57,475 --> 00:54:59,975
目を覚まして　あなたの憧れ
wake up to your aspiration.

185
00:56:17,797 --> 00:56:20,697
風に吹かれて
Blown by the wind,

186
00:56:20,697 --> 00:56:23,697
誰も気づかぬよ
without anyone noticing,

187
00:56:23,697 --> 00:56:25,797
区別がつかない
I can't tell the difference

188
00:56:25,797 --> 00:56:29,097
モノクロの世界
in this monochrome world.

189
00:56:29,497 --> 00:56:32,397
色を足しても
Even if I add color,

190
00:56:32,397 --> 00:56:35,397
何も見えなくて
I can't see anything,

191
00:56:35,397 --> 00:56:38,097
まるで私は
as if I had...

192
00:56:38,097 --> 00:56:42,397
息を止めていた
stopped breathing.

193
00:56:45,597 --> 00:56:48,197
もういいよ 遠くても
It's okay now, even from afar,

194
00:56:48,197 --> 00:56:52,597
叶えたい 私は
I want to make it come true.

195
00:56:52,597 --> 00:56:55,397
この世界を 今も
This world, even now,

196
00:56:55,397 --> 00:56:58,397
抱きしめていたいのに
I want to keep holding it tight,

197
00:56:58,397 --> 00:57:01,397
夢のキャンバスに
yet on the canvas of my dreams,

198
00:57:01,397 --> 00:57:04,597
描き続けていく意味を
the meaning of continuing to draw

199
00:57:04,597 --> 00:57:08,497
この胸に 輝いている
is shining in this chest.

200
00:57:08,497 --> 00:57:13,197
ストーリー
Story

201
00:57:22,397 --> 00:57:25,397
ありふれることに
There's no meaning

202
00:57:25,397 --> 00:57:28,397
意味などないけど
in things being ordinary,

203
00:57:28,397 --> 00:57:31,397
拾い集めた
but the fragments I gathered

204
00:57:31,397 --> 00:57:34,597
欠片失うの
are being lost.

205
00:57:34,597 --> 00:57:39,597
そして夜は その冷たさを
And the night, it melts that coldness,

206
00:57:39,597 --> 00:57:44,497
溶かして手を伸ばした
as I reached out my hand.

207
00:57:44,897 --> 00:57:47,397
もういいの 遠くても
It's okay now, even from afar,

208
00:57:47,397 --> 00:57:51,497
届けたい 私は
I want to reach it.

209
00:57:51,497 --> 00:57:54,397
埋め尽くす 涙も
I'm releasing these tears

210
00:57:54,397 --> 00:57:57,397
抱きしめていたいのに
even though I want to hold them tight,

211
00:57:57,397 --> 00:58:00,397
夢のキャンバスに
yet on the canvas of my dreams,

212
00:58:00,397 --> 00:58:03,497
心込めるのは
what I put my heart into

213
00:58:03,497 --> 00:58:08,497
この空に 描き出していく
is beginning to be drawn in this sky.

214
00:58:08,497 --> 00:58:12,597
ストーリー
Story

215
00:58:21,497 --> 00:58:26,497
そして夜は その冷たさを
And the night, it melts that coldness,

216
