00:58:31,797 --> 00:58:34,597
もういいの 遠くても
It's okay now, even from afar,

218
00:58:34,597 --> 00:58:38,797
叶えたい 私は
I want to make it come true.

219
00:58:38,797 --> 00:58:41,397
この世界を 今も
I'm wrapping this world,

220
00:58:41,397 --> 00:58:44,397
言葉で包んだ
even now, in words.

221
00:58:44,397 --> 00:58:47,397
夢のキャンバスに
On the canvas of my dreams,

222
00:58:47,397 --> 00:58:50,397
色を足していく
I'm adding colors,

223
00:58:50,397 --> 00:58:53,597
この胸に 今輝いて
shining in this chest now.

224
00:58:56,597 --> 00:58:59,597
強くなくてもいい
It's okay if I'm not strong,

225
00:58:59,597 --> 00:59:02,597
壊れかけてもいい
it's okay if I'm falling apart,

226
00:59:02,597 --> 00:59:07,497
この心は永遠に羽ばたいて
this heart will take flight for eternity.

227
00:59:07,897 --> 00:59:10,897
響くように
So it may resonate,

228
00:59:10,897 --> 00:59:14,597
塗り替えていく 鮮やかな
I'm repainting it into a vivid...

229
00:59:14,597 --> 00:59:19,397
ストーリー
Story

230
00:59:43,897 --> 00:59:49,697
Hello everyone!

231
00:59:49,897 --> 00:59:57,897
It is Day 2 of Drawn to Dawn!

232
00:59:58,397 --> 01:00:05,597
Yes, yes, welcome to Day 2 of Takanashi Kiara and Ninomae Ina'nis's first concert, Drawn to Dawn!

233
01:00:05,240 --> 01:00:07,540
Are you guys enjoying the show so far?

234
01:00:11,740 --> 01:00:14,740
You know, I was really...

235
01:00:14,740 --> 01:00:18,740
I want to talk about TakoTako first because...

236
01:00:18,740 --> 01:00:24,040
...yesterday, I heard you guys sing along to the instrumental...

237
01:00:24,040 --> 01:00:28,240
...and I was like, "Uh... ooh, I feel bad for not singing on Day 1."

238
01:00:28,240 --> 01:00:32,740
But you know, I knew I was opening for, you know, Day 2...

239
01:00:32,740 --> 01:00:37,240
...so I couldn't have thought of a better song to open than TakoTako.

240
01:00:37,240 --> 01:00:39,740
Hope you guys had fun singing it!

241
01:00:39,740 --> 01:00:42,240
Thank you again!

242
01:00:42,240 --> 01:00:46,040
And of course, I sang two of my senpais' songs...

243
01:00:46,040 --> 01:00:49,440
...Sencho's "Dead Man's Chest"...

244
01:00:49,440 --> 01:00:53,740
...and Towa-sama's "Palette".

245
01:00:53,740 --> 01:00:59,240
I specifically wanted to choose their songs because...

246
01:00:59,240 --> 01:01:03,740
...they're senpais that I really look up to...

247
01:01:03,740 --> 01:01:08,740
...and I always feel like my journey here wouldn't have been possible...

248
01:01:08,740 --> 01:01:14,240
...if I didn't discover my senpais many, many years ago.

249
01:01:14,240 --> 01:01:19,740
And I always wanted to pay respect to the path they paved for us.

250
01:01:19,740 --> 01:01:22,740
So, yeah, I hope you guys enjoyed it!

251
01:01:22,740 --> 01:01:26,740
I'm so nervous again!

252
01:01:30,240 --> 01:01:35,040
And, you know, I of course didn't really tell you guys...

253
01:01:35,040 --> 01:01:37,740
...specifically what penlight colors to use...

254
01:01:37,740 --> 01:01:42,240
...but I knew that you guys would get my message...

255
01:01:42,240 --> 01:01:46,240
...because we share a brain cell, right? Right?

256
01:01:46,240 --> 01:01:50,240
And yeah, so... well, um...

257
01:01:50,240 --> 01:01:54,240
...now going by the different setlist...

258
01:01:54,240 --> 01:01:58,240
...because we have different setlists for Day 1 and Day 2...

259
01:01:58,240 --> 01:02:01,740
...so, going by the process of elimination...

260
01:02:01,740 --> 01:02:06,040
...we have a couple of songs from my new EP left, actually.

261
01:02:06,040 --> 01:02:09,740
Who here bought my EP?

262
01:02:09,740 --> 01:02:13,740
Yay! Thank you so much!

263
01:02:13,740 --> 01:02:18,740
I hope you were lucky to get an autograph. I tried to sign as much as possible...

264
01:02:18,740 --> 01:02:23,740
...but I knew, you know, sometimes you can't be lucky.

265
01:02:23,740 --> 01:02:27,240
Thank you, thank you!

266
01:02:27,240 --> 01:02:31,740
But yeah, I want you guys to have even more fun than before today!

267
01:02:31,740 --> 01:02:35,740
I mean, you always have fun, so that's good.

268
01:02:35,740 --> 01:02:39,740
But um... yeah! Sing along, have fun...

269
01:02:39,740 --> 01:02:44,740
...and I always think that a live stage is where not only me performing...

270
01:02:44,740 --> 01:02:49,740
...is creating the performance, but you guys as well.

271
01:02:49,740 --> 01:02:53,740
You really help everyone with that special experience.

272
01:02:53,740 --> 01:02:58,740
So let's create an unforgettable memory together today, okay?

273
01:02:58,740 --> 01:03:01,740
Nyah!

274
01:03:01,740 --> 01:03:05,740
Anyways, I would also like to shout out...

275
01:03:05,740 --> 01:03:10,740
to those watching at home and at the live viewing in the cinema.

276
01:03:10,740 --> 01:03:14,240
Hello, hello to you again!

277
01:03:14,240 --> 01:03:17,740
And also, to the lovely girls doing a watchalong right now.

278
01:03:17,740 --> 01:03:21,240
Hi guys! Thank you!

279
01:03:21,240 --> 01:03:25,740
IRyS, EN, and everyone else doing the watchalong.

280
01:03:25,740 --> 01:03:30,740
Thank you, thank you! You know, I'm always amazed by everyone's support.

281
01:03:30,740 --> 01:03:36,240
And really without the support of Holo EN members as well...

282
01:03:36,240 --> 01:03:41,740
...I wouldn't have had the confidence to stand here today.

283
01:03:41,740 --> 01:03:44,740
Thank you, I love you!

284
01:03:44,740 --> 01:03:50,240
And of course, I would like to remind you guys about the hashtag...

285
01:03:50,240 --> 01:03:54,740
...for today's concert as well, #TakoTori1stConcert.

286
01:03:54,740 --> 01:03:59,240
As usual, post your thoughts about it, post the screenshots.

287
01:03:59,240 --> 01:04:01,740
No videos, no videos!

288
01:04:01,740 --> 01:04:05,240
Post the screenshots and, you know, Kiara and I...

289
01:04:05,240 --> 01:04:09,740
...whenever we have time, we've been checking the hashtag.

290
01:04:09,740 --> 01:04:13,740
And of course after as well, I want to hear what you guys thought about the live.

291
01:04:13,740 --> 01:04:16,740
So, yeah! Thank you, thank you!

292
01:04:16,740 --> 01:04:20,740
And unlike yesterday, first MC means...

293
01:04:20,740 --> 01:04:26,240
...I unfortunately have to bid farewell to those watching the sneak peek on YouTube.

294
01:04:26,240 --> 01:04:29,240
I'm sorry!

295
01:04:29,240 --> 01:04:33,740
But if you want to keep the party going...

296
01:04:33,740 --> 01:04:37,740
...head to the streaming site via the description or the comment.

297
01:04:37,740 --> 01:04:41,240
I don't know where the comment is!

298
01:04:41,240 --> 01:04:45,740
But I know that some of you guys won't get a chance...

299
01:04:45,740 --> 01:04:50,740
...to see my new outfit that I revealed yesterday.

300
01:04:50,740 --> 01:04:55,240
So, I thought maybe I'll do something...

301
01:04:55,240 --> 01:04:59,740
...maybe you guys can help me transition into the new costume here...

302
01:04:59,740 --> 01:05:03,240
...so that even those of you...

303
01:05:02,787 --> 01:05:04,787
...and YouTube Tiramisu can see!

304
01:05:05,287 --> 01:05:06,987
All right, so I'm gonna count down from three.

305
01:05:06,987 --> 01:05:08,287
Count down with me, okay?

306
01:05:08,287 --> 01:05:11,287
And I will switch into the new outfit for you guys to see.

307
01:05:12,787 --> 01:05:13,787
Ready?

308
01:05:15,787 --> 01:05:17,287
Ready? Give me a "wah" if you're ready!

309
01:05:20,087 --> 01:05:21,287
All right, all right, all right.

310
01:05:21,287 --> 01:05:22,287
All right, here we go.

311
01:05:22,287 --> 01:05:23,287
Three!

312
01:05:23,287 --> 01:05:24,287
Two!

313
01:05:24,287 --> 01:05:25,287
One!

314
01:05:25,287 --> 01:05:26,287
Hah!

315
01:05:28,287 --> 01:05:30,287
Tada!

316
01:05:31,787 --> 01:05:33,787
Thank you, thank you, thank you!

317
01:05:37,287 --> 01:05:39,287
All right, it's time to move on to the next song.

318
01:05:39,787 --> 01:05:42,787
And I think this song also fits the starry stage perfectly.

319
01:05:44,287 --> 01:05:45,787
Not that one yet, but...

320
01:05:46,787 --> 01:05:49,787
But this one is from one of my favorite franchises.

321
01:05:50,287 --> 01:05:51,787
So I hope you guys listen.

322
01:05:51,787 --> 01:05:54,287
Anyways, the song will fit the starry stage perfectly.

323
01:05:54,787 --> 01:05:56,787
Please, give it a listen.

324
01:06:03,787 --> 01:06:08,787
無料パートの放送は終了しました。ご視聴ありがとうございました！
The sneak peek part of the show has ended. Thank you for watching!

